# Cloudflare Pages routing. Rewrites point at directories (not index.html
# suffix) to let Pages' native directory-index handling resolve them,
# avoiding the pretty-URL redirect loop. Order matters: specific rules first,
# explicit catch-all last so Pages doesn't auto-inject its own SPA fallback
# above ours.

/embed/*     /embed/      200
/configure/* /configure/  200
/holder/*    /holder/     200
/gallery     /gallery/    200
/play        /play/       200
/*           /index.html  200
